Maze Adventure Requirements
user must be able to move up, down, left, and right – mandatory, functional
user must start the game at a fixed starting position – mandatory, functional
exit tile must end the level when reached – mandatory, functional
player health must be displayed on screen – mandatory, functional
monsters must appear at random open locations in the maze – mandatory, functional
player must battle a monster when landing on its tile – mandatory, functional
Items must be collected when the player moves onto their tile – mandatory, functional
game must save progress after each level is completed – mandatory, functional
may include health potions that restore player health – optional, functional
monsters must deal damage when attacking the player – mandatory, functional
